arguments.value: must require an ACCEPT header specifying the JSON API media type
must respond to a successful request with an object
must respond to an unsuccessful request with a JSON object containing a collection keyed by "errors" in the top level
must require a content-type header of application/vnd.api+json
must require a single resource object as primary data
must require primary data to have a type member
may accept a client-generated ID along with a request to create a resource
must return 403 Forbidden in response to an unsupported request using a client-generated ID
must respond with 201 and  include a Location header identifying the location of the new resource
must include a document containing the primary resource created
must make the self link and Location header the same
must return 409 Conflict when processing a request to create a resource with an existing client-generated ID
must return 409 Conflict when processing a request where the type does not match the endpoint
